012e1_d135013e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xpx1665703194081__p_d135014e1_d135015e1_d135016e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation DISCONNECT</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpx1665703194081__section_wt3_k5d_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d104724e57\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpx1665703194081__section_hkp_m5d_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d104724e66\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to 0. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpx1665703194081__section_smv_n5d_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d104724e82\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpx1665703194081__section_dl4_45d_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d104724e91\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">DISCONNECT</span> operation closes the connection to the Uniface\n        Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=